<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="breathless-adj">breathless <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'breθləs/    美 /'breθləs/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>气喘吁吁的；呼吸急促的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I was breathless after climbing the stairs. 
爬上楼梯后我气喘吁吁。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>breathlessly /'breθləsli/ adv   </p></div>